joomatari adag: Daraasadda qaab-dhismeedka joomatari iyo dhismooyinka ka soo baxa, ama lagu sharraxay, tirooyinka adag
tirooyinka adag: Nambarada foomka a + bi halka a iyo b ay yihiin tirooyinka dhabta ah
qayb dhab ah: Erayga ku jira tiro kakan oo aan ku jirin unugga mala-awaalka ah qodob ahaan
qayb khayaali ah: Qaybta nambarka adag ee leh halbeegga mala-awaalka ah qodob ahaan
kala duwanaansho adag: Meel bannaan oo joomatari adag ah oo guud ahaan qalooca iyo dusha sare
noocyo aljabrada adag: Meel bannaan oo joomatari adag oo xal u ah isla'egyada badan
dhismooyinka holomorphic: Dhismayaasha joomatari adag oo kakan-kala duwan
barnaamijka model ugu yar: Barnaamij ku jira joomatari kakan oo loogu talagalay kala soocida noocyada kala duwan ee aljabrada adag
boosaska moduli: Meel bannaan oo joomatari adag oo cabbiraya nooc ka mid ah shay joomatari
mala-awaal calabi: Malo-awaal ku jira joomatari adag oo ay caddeysay Shing-Tung Yau oo ku saabsan jiritaanka nooc gaar ah oo mitir ah oo kala duwan
hitchin-kobayashi waraaqaha: Xidhiidhka joomatari kakan ee u dhexeeya xidhmooyinka vector ee holomorphic deggan iyo xalalka isla'egta kala duwan
waraaqaha hodge nonabelian: Warqadaha joomatari kakan ee u dhexeeya noocyada kala duwan ee noocyada kala duwan ee kakan iyo noocyada qaar ee qaab-dhismeedka aljabrada
kahler-einstein metrics: Noocyo gaar ah oo cabbiro kala duwan oo kakan oo qanciya xaalad gaar ah
